# Bound For Glory

## Run locally

```bash
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
python3 scripts/preflight_check.py
python3 -m streamlit run app.py
```

Open: http://localhost:8501

## Before deploy

```bash
python3 scripts/preflight_check.py
```

Optional multiplayer database: set `DATABASE_URL` in `.streamlit/secrets.toml` (never commit real keys).

## Podcast audio (NXT Unfiltered)

```bash
./setup_podcast_audio.sh
```

OpenAI voices (optional): copy `.env.example` to `.env` and set `OPENAI_API_KEY`.
